title: Bug 120315 - Display property 'none' not taking effect in new PDF emitter
OB: The display property of an item set to 'none' is not having any effect in the new PDF emitter.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the application and navigate to the page containing the item with the display property set to 'none'. 
2. Verify that the item is still visible in the generated PDF. 
3. Change the display property of the item to a different value, such as 'block', and regenerate the PDF. 
4. Confirm that the item is now visible in the PDF when the display property is not set to 'none'.
